This is the base codeigniter installation that I start a project with.
It includes many of the common libraries, helpers, assets that I use in
most projects.

Codeigniter 1.7.3
    - _base
    - application
    - assets
        - compressed
            - css
            - js
        - css
            - ie
        - images
        - javascript
            - ie
            - jquery
                - plugin
                - theme
    - ci-1.7.3
    - logs



CI Libraries:
    - Assetlibpro          http://code.google.com/p/assetlib-pro/
    - Authorize_net        http://idealws.com
    - Orbit                http://dhorrigan.com (CI.php)
    - Flare                http://bitbucket.org/jamierumbelow/flare
    - Formation            http://dhorrigan.com
    - Ion_Auth             http://github.com/benedmunds/CodeIgniter-Ion-Auth
    - MY_Config            http://sajjadhossain.com/2008/10/27/ssl-https-urls-and-codeigniter/
    - MY_Controller        http://github.com/jamierumbelow/codeigniter-base-controller
    - UhOh                 http://dhorrigan.com (MY_Exceptions.php)
    - MY_Form_validation   unique(), required_dependency()
    - MY_Model             http://github.com/philsturgeon/codeigniter-base-model
    - MY_Pagination        create_tabbed_links() for using with tab hashes I.E. #tab-2, #tab-3, etc
    - Numbertowords        http://codeigniter.com/forums/viewthread/174027/#826704
    
CI Helpers
    - ajax                 
    - common_lists         
    - datediff             
    - randcode             
    - relative_time        
    - secure_url           Uses MY_Config to get secure_site_url()
    
CI Models
    - ion_auth_model
    
CI Plugins
    - csstidy              http://cdburnerxp.se/cssparse/csstidy/
    - jsmin                http://code.google.com/p/jsmin-php/
    - to_excel_pi          
    
CI Hooks
    - uhoh                 http://dhorrigan.com
    - Yielder              http://hasin.wordpress.com/2007/03/05/adding-yield-codeigniter/
    
